                        <p class="text_bold">What is SEO? </p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">Search Engine Optimization is all about knowing and implementing what can make your website visible. It focuses on attracting visitors organically by ranking higher in Google searches. This can be achieved through optimizing your website and content according to several factors that affect the rankings. </p>
                        <p class="text_bold">Why is ranking high on search engines important for your website?</p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">Every day more than 3 billion searches are made on Google alone for SEO. This means there must be hundreds and thousands of people searching for answers every second that are relevant to your business. So for all the time you are not ranked high on Google, you miss out on visitors, leads, and eventually, money. </p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">By optimizing your site according to the relevant keywords, you can tap into the enormous potential which the Internet offers for your business. This also ensures a smooth user experience for your new visitors as well as existing customers. </p>
                        <p class="text_bold">What are we going to offer? </p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">We know how valuable customers are for your business. To make yourself visible amidst the chaos, your online presence requires clear planning and implementation of multiple strategies. This can boost your visibility on the Internet and significantly increase your sales too. </p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">Always remember that SEO is not just for ranking higher on the search engines. It is also aimed at providing a better user experience for everybody that visits your website.  </p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">At <span class="text_bold">Exult IT Solutions</span>, we have a team of professionals with years of experience in the field of digital marketing. Our experts have worked with several brands and businesses to provide them with effective marketing solutions. The plans and strategies are made after we conduct an in-depth analysis of your business, requirements as well as your customer base. This rigorous research enables us to understand what is required and what exactly do your business needs. </p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">Our SEO strategy is planned by experts and involves all the necessary procedures to rank your website higher in the relevant Google searches. This includes two major components:-</p>
                        <p class="text_bold">On-Page Optimization</p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">As the name goes, this includes all the adjustments and modifications made on the website. This is inarguably the most visible aspect of SEO. A website has several elements that significantly impact the visitor’s decision-making as well as their user experience.</p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">A major part of the on-page SEO includes optimizing content available on your website. This requires keyword research, optimized titles, meta descriptions, and tags. Several other features such as improving URLs, images, creating internal and external links also require modification. </p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">Having a great website is useless at the end of the day if it does not performs well. Loading speed is an important thing to keep in mind while doing on-page optimization. </p>
                        <p class="text_bold">Off-Page Optimization</p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">Off-page optimization goes beyond the work done on the website. This strategy includes building your brand’s credibility by generating enough backlinks on various reputed websites and platforms. When users come across your web link on a reputable website, it would create their trust in your brand. </p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">Google does not entertain spam redirects to your website and one should always avoid this. Thus, creating relevant backlinks requires proper research and analysis. These links should be optimized according to subject relevance, anchor text, link location, etc.</p>
                        <p class="col_about_p">A brand can take advantage of this strategy using social media, emails, guest blogging, and much more. This way you can reach a wider audience without sending out spam links to attract visitors to your website.</p>
                        <p class="text_bold">Our services also include:</p>
                        <p class="text_bold">Mobile Optimization </p>
