                        <p class="col_about_p">The term Technical SEO refers to website optimization according to crawlers and web index. A proper technical SEO can ensure that the website is smoothly indexed by the search engines, preferably Google. This includes optimizing the URL structure, adding an SSL certificate and HTTPS, better website speed, registration with webmaster tools, etc. </p>
